      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just finished changing the brake pads on my 2018 camry but now when i pull into my driveway i hear this really high pitched squealing sound coming from the front end. not sure if i messed something up or if it means the sensor is bad or something? any idea if its the caliper or just the pads settling?",
